u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEST-NYT     04-14 0013
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEST-NYT </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   This is test of wire transmission from New York Times circuit
</P>
