Tang isn't? What about baby diapers bearing taxes while similar
items for adults are tax-free? And what's the reason that
honey-roasted peanuts are taxed but salted peanuts are not? ``We
haven't the slightest idea,'' says New York state Sen. Roy Goodman,
who conducted a hearing Tuesday on the sales tax. By JAMES M.
ODATO.
