European Union holds a summit on Kosovo. The plan has key role for
the United Nations and Kofi Annan, its secretary-general, who is
attending the meeting. The plan calls for a halt in air strikes if
Yugoslavia withdraws its forces from Kosovo. By Craig R. Whitney.
</P>
<P>
