points, or 0.3 percent, and the Nasdaq index was up 6 points, or
0.2 percent. Elsewhere, prices rose 0.3 percent in Tokyo and fell
0.6 percent in Hong Kong. They decreased 0.7 percent in Frankfurt,
0.3 percent in London and 0.4 percent in Mexico. Stocks in Brazil
