Trainer: Bob Baffert. Last race: Won Santa Anita Derby April 3.
Next race: Kentucky Derby at Churchill Downs May 1.
</P>
<P>
   --MENIFEE. Sire: Harlan. Jockey: Pat Day. Trainer: Elliott
Walden. Last race: Won Blue Grass at Keeneland April 10. Next race:
Kentucky Derby.
</P>
<P>
   --ADONIS. Sire: Kris S. Jockey: Jorge Chavez. Trainer: Nick
Zito. Last race: Won Wood Memorial at Aqueduct April 10. Next race:
Kentucky Derby.
</P>
<P>
   --ALJABR. Sire: Storm Cat. Jockey: Frankie Dettori. Trainer:
Saeed Bin Suroor. Last race: Won Dubai Derby Trial II at Nad al
Sheba Racecourse April 8. Next race: Kentucky Derby.
</P>
<P>
   --WORLDLY MANNER. Sire: Riverman. Jockey: Jerry Bailey. Trainer:
Bin Suroor. Last race: Won Dubai Derby Trail I at Nad Al Sheba
Racecourse March 21. Next race: Kentucky Derby.
</P>
<P>
   --PRIME TIMBER. Sire: Sultry Song. Jockey: David Flores.
Trainer: Baffert. Last race: Second in Santa Anita Derby. Next
race: Kentucky Derby.
</P>
