<P>
   GLF-UGA-GOLF _ The Georgia men's golf team, ranked No. 1 in the
nation, is one of the favorites to win the SEC championship this
weekend in Lexington, Ky. The Bulldogs have two of the SEC's top
players in Ryuji Imada and Michael Morrison, but most of the team's
success can be attributed to coach Chris Haack. Since arriving at
Georgia in 1996, Haack has been a tireless promoter of the program
and has helped to rebuild a program that had slipped before his
arrival. (Towers, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15. WITH PHOTO.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-GATECH-GOLF _ Advancing the Georgia Tech golf team heading
into the ACC championships this weekend. (Clemons, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 6-8.
</P>
