<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-14 17:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8200 &Cx1f; tie-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CIR-VOICE-WEB-NYT &LR;      04-14 1218
