   JOKES
</P>
<P>
   Q: April showers bring May flowers, but what do May flowers
bring?
</P>
<P>
   A: Pilgrims! Kate Strickland.
</P>
<P>
   Q: What kind of dog runs a fever?
</P>
<P>
   A: A hot dog! Krystal Johnson.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Why did the Boy Scouts take a pitcher on their camping trip?
</P>
<P>
   A: To pitch the tent! Joanna Reasoner.
</P>
<P>
   Q: How can you tell if a calendar is popular?
</P>
<P>
   A: It has a lot of dates! Andrea Cowan.
</P>
<P>
   Q: How do you paint a rabbit?
</P>
<P>
   A: With hare spray! Jenna Stevenson.
</P>
