<P>
   ``THE RUGRATS MOVIE''
</P>
<P>
   Starring: Voices of Whoopi Goldberg, David Spade, Tim Curry and
songs by No Doubt, Lisa Loeb and Beck, Busta Rhymes.
</P>
<P>
   Plot: This animated movie is based on the popular Nickelodeon
cable network show. Tommy gets a new little brother, Baby Dil, and
his loud demands have Tommy, Chuckie, Phil and Lil going bonkers.
They decide to ship him back and wind up going deep into the woods,
where they have to cope with bad weather, monkeys, a wolf and an
