29,028-foot trek to the top of Mount Everest. The film, made by
special IMAX cameras that were carried up the mountain, shows
snow-covered peaks, sheer faces of treacherous ice and deep chasms,
which climbers cross using ladders. Narrator is Liam Neeson and
music is by George Harrison.
</P>
