<P>
   DROWN (EPHRATA, Wash.) _ Five boys died when the car carrying
them plunged into a swift-flowing irrigation canal and sank upside
down just outside this Columbia Basin community in Eastern
Washington. The boys' two mothers managed to swim to safety in
Tuesday's accident.
